channel.title: Silab Client (V3)
channel.description:
Hello It's about Silabsoft Client (V3) Its dead... I can't use it longer: [font=Verdana]To fix this try the following (in order): 1. Try clising all open web-browsers windows, and reloading 2. Try clearing your web-browsers cache from tools >> Internet options 3. Try useing a different game world 4. Try rebooting your computer 5. Try selecting a different version of java from the play-game menu[/font] Well, I cant select another world, I tried to close all browsers B4 playing, I tried to reboot my computer, I can't select another version of Java And i cleared already my web-browsers cache... What can i do? and Yes, i've got enough RS2 servers downloaded, But i even cant try to login, it stops at ''Unpacking Config'' I've got another error too: [font=Verdana]RS2 user client - releasy #317 Midi device unavailable! [b]Error: loaderror Unpacking config 86[/b][/font] Well, Somebody know what's the problem? I dont have any idea, Thank you! - Jussel
Maybe is it updating?
